Merge sample/feature data

merge_sdata.Rd

Merge sample/feature data

merge_fdata(object, df, by = "feature_id")

merge_sdata(object, df, by = "sample_id")

Arguments

object

SummarizedExperiment
df

data.frame
by

string

Value

SummarizedExperiment

Examples

require(magrittr)
file <- download_data('halama18.metabolon.xlsx')
object <- read_metabolon(file)

#> 	Read: ~/autonomicscache/datasets/halama18/halama18.metabolon.xlsx
#> 		Infer design from sample_ids
#> 		Guess replicate values from sampleids: ctrl_h10_R1 => R1
#> 		Log2 transform
#> 	Add PCA
#> 		Retain 391/391 features: non-zero, non-NA, and non-NaN for some sample
#> 		Run limma
#> 		Retain 96/96 samples: ~!is.na(~subgroup)
object %<>% merge_sdata( data.frame(sample_id = object$sample_id,
                                    number = seq_along(object$sample_id)))
sdata(object)
